---
title: Verification Wizard
---
<main>
  <section>
    <form id="msform">
      <ul id="progressbar">
        <li class="active"></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
        <li></li>
      </ul>

      <fieldset id="activation-number">
        <h3>
          Enter the sixteen digit account number on your eLEND Mortgage Card:
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip tooltip-image">
              <img src="images/cc.png">
              <p>Your account number is the number on the front of your Copperline Account Card. If you don’t have your card, call 800-260-4897 ext 2 and activate your account through a call center agent.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <div class="inputs half-input">
          <field>
            <input type="tel" name="cardNumber" placeholder="1111-1111-1111-1111">
          </field>
        </div>
          <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button add-break" value="Next" />
      </fieldset>
      <fieldset id="confirm-company">
        <div class="text-block">
          <br>
          <h3>Is this Terri Murray from San Clemente, California?</h3>
          <h3>(Nice home.)</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="image-block">
          <img src="images/home2.png">
          <br><br>
        </div>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="visa-card">
        <div class="text-block">
          <h3>Well Terri, Zillow estimates your home value at $389,330, that’s pretty good.</h3>
          <h3>Do you think that’s about right?</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="image-block">
          <img src="images/map.png">
        </div>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="confirm-name">
        <h3>According to Experian, you owe $278,093.00 on your mortgage with Quicken Loans and your payments are $725/mo.</h3>
        <h3>Is that “about” right?</h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="option-list" class="three-buttons">
        <h3>Great Terri, you’ve got two options.</h3>
        <div class="wrapper">
          <ul>
            <li>1. You can reduce your monthly payment (refinance).</li>
            <li>2. You can get cash back (Refinance & Cash Back).</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <h3>Which option would you like to see?</h3>
          <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Refinance" />
          <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="Refinance & Cash Back" />
          <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="Both" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="shipping-address">
        <h3>You could get $88,989 in cash (use it for home improvements, pay off debt, purchase a new car, etc.) and your total monthly payment would be $678/mo.</h3>
        <h3>Which option works best for you?</h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Refinance" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="Home Equity" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="option-home-worth">
        <h3>Great, that’s an excellent option.</h3>
        <h3>Let’s get started. There are no long applications since we already have most of the information we need. You simply need to verify this information. It only takes a minute.</h3>
        <h3>Ready to go?</h3>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="experian">
        <h3>
          <span>Terri</span>, for your protection, we need to verify your identity through Experian, is this ok?
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip">
              <p>We use the Experian credit report to verify your identity and to provide you with a pre-qualification for credit for your company. This is a “soft pull” of your report for pre-screening purposes. It will not affect your credit score or put an inquiry on your report. We will reserve the right to pull your credit report if you choose to accept the terms and conditions of our loan offer.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <p>This will not affect your FICO credit score and there will be no inquiry on your credit report.  View <a href="#" target="_blank">terms and conditions</a>.</p>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Yes" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="No" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="address">
        <h3>
          <span>Terri</span>, enter your home address and date of birth so we can verify this information with the Experian credit report.
          <div class="tooltip-item">
            ?
            <div class="tooltip">
              <p>We use the  your home address to match with your Experian credit report. This is a “soft pull” of your report for pre-screening purposes. It will not affect your credit score or put an inquiry on your report. </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </h3>
        <label>Home Address</label>
        <div class="inputs full-input">
          <field>
            <input type="text" name="street" placeholder="Street" />
          </field>
          <field>
            <input type="text" name="suite" placeholder="Suite" />
          </field>
        </div>
        <div class="inputs third-input">
          <field>
            <input type="text" name="city" placeholder="City" />
          </field>
          <field>
            <input type="text" name="state" placeholder="State" />
          </field>
          <field>
            <input type="tel" name="zipCode" placeholder="Zip Code" />
          </field>
        </div>
        <label>Date of Birth</label>
        <div class="inputs half-input">
          <field>
            <input type="tel" name="birthDate" placeholder="MM/DD/YYYY"/>
          </field>
        </div>
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button" value="Next" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="option-loan" class="radio-group">
        <h3>Which of these three addresses is one of the places you lived prior to your purchase of your San Clemente home:</h3>
        <div class="next">
          <label class="radio"><input id="radio1" type="radio" name="radios"><span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>10 Spinnaker Drive, Carlsbad, CA </label>
          <label class="radio"><input id="radio2" type="radio" name="radios"><span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>1909 Hawthorne Drive, Sudbury, MA</label>
          <label class="radio"><input id="radio3" type="radio" name="radios"><span class="outer"><span class="inner"></span></span>344 Palm Canyon, Los Angles, CA</label>
        </div>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="activation-number">
        <h3>Terri, tell us about your income:</h3>
        <div class="inputs half-input">
          <field>
            <label>Employer Name</label>
            <input type="tel" name="employerName">
          </field>
          <field>
            <label>Yearly Income</label>
            <input type="tel" name="annualRevenue" placeholder="">
          </field>
        </div>
          <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button add-break" value="Next" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="results">
        <h3>Congratulations, Terri. We’ve verified your identity, checked your credit, and confirmed your equity. Here’s your new loan:</h3>
        <div class="wrapper">
          <table>
            <tr>
              <td>Refinance Amount:</td>
              <td>$300,341</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Cash Back:</td>
              <td>$88,989</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Monthly Payment:</td>
              <td>$678</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Closing Fees:</td>
              <td>$250</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>Interest Rate:</td>
              <td>3.99%</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>

        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button add-break" value="Accept" />
        <input type="button" name="next" class="next action-button inactive-button" value="Save for Later" />
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset id="complete">
        <h3>Congratulations, Terri. We are looking forward to working with you. Here is my contact information:</h3>
        <div class="contact-block">
          <img src="images/sharon.jpg" class="point-of-contact">
          <div class="contact-info">
            <p><strong>Sharon Boyer</strong> <br>800-260-4897 x713<br>sharon@copperlineusa.com</p>
            <p>Branch Office: Chicago</p>
            <img src="images/elend-mortgage.png" class="grey-logo">
          </div>
        </div>
      </fieldset>
    </form>
  </section>

